sj = StringJoiner(prefix='[', suffix=']')
sj.add('e1').add('e2').add(3)
del sj[1]
self.assertEqual('[e1,3]', str(sj))
expected__repr__ = (
    '{"separator": ",", "prefix": "[", "suffix": "]", "nelem": 2, "str_length": 6, "elements": ["e1", "3"]}'
    )
self.assertEqual(expected__repr__, sj.__repr__())
